  "description": "Task 9 (2026-07-12): the old issueLifecycle FSM (tatara_lifecycle_state/tatara_lifecycle_transition_total/tatara_lifecycle_seconds/tatara_mrci_wait_seconds/tatara_lifecycle_giveup_total/tatara_lifecycle_handover_total/tatara_lifecycle_idle_stop_total/tatara_lifecycle_implement_empty_retry_total) dies WITH the task-centric redesign (contract L.1) and none of it is on scripts/metrics_allowlist.txt. Every panel below is repointed onto the new Task stage machine (operator_task_stage, operator_task_stage_age_seconds, operator_task_parked_total, operator_agent_pod_ttl_expired_total) where a successor metric exists; three panels with no successor (transition rate, full-lifecycle latency, MRCI wait) were deleted outright rather than left querying a dead metric. CROSS-REPO DEPENDENCY D1 (operator_task_terminal_total surviving with stage+stageReason+kind replacing phase) is UNVERIFIED as of this edit - the operator worktree has not landed the swap (internal/obs/task_metrics.go:31-33 still declares kind,phase,reason). The Terminal Task Outcomes panels are written on the D1 assumption; re-verify against the merged operator before this ships.",
  "editable": true,
  "fiscalYearStartMonth": 0,
  "graphTooltip": 0,
  "id": null,
  "links": [],
